Cynic is MIT-licensed. Bundled third-party data under vendor/ retains its
own license:

  vendor/unicode/   Unicode Character Database (UCD data files), Unicode,
                    Inc. License Agreement.
                    https://www.unicode.org/license.txt

  vendor/test262/   ECMAScript Test Suite, BSD-3-Clause (with Ecma
                    International notices). git submodule pinned to
                    tc39/test262. https://github.com/tc39/test262

The vendored data is build-time only (the UCD files generate the Unicode
tables; test262 is the conformance suite) — none of it is shipped as
code visible to user JS.
